"* ABA on (joiner slot, target slot, park_epoch): a disarmed deadline timer from a
"* finished timeout fires on a *reused* pair of task slots with a matching epoch.
"* Correct behavior: prints ok1 then ok2 (~1s). Buggy: t2 hits TimeoutError instantly.
var t1 = Task.spawn:{ Async.timeout:200 do:{ Async.sleep:5; 'ok1' } };
t1.join.print;
var t2 = Task.spawn:{ Async.timeout:60000 do:{ Async.sleep:1000; 'ok2' } };
var r = { t2.join }.catch:{ |e| 'BUG: ' + e.s };
r.print;
'done'.print
